OL,3,CTaskforce take on problems facing
OL,4,CLondon's late night economy
OL,6,FNew rules to support London's pubs and
OL,7,Fclubs could be coming to the Capital,
OL,8,Fafter the London Nightlife Taskforce
OL,9,Fpublished its final report today.
OL,11,FThe independent review, commissioned
OL,12,Fby mayor Sir Sadiq Khan, lays out 23
OL,13,Frecommendations to protect and grow
OL,14,Fnight-time industries. The proposals
OL,15,Fcover licensing, planning, transport
OL,16,Fand public safety.
