OL,3,CTaskforce take on problems facing
OL,4,CLondon's late night economy
OL,6,FThe Taskforce also encourages the
OL,7,Fcreation of an independent Nightlife
OL,8,FCommission to be a unified voice for
OL,9,Fthe industry and see that the
OL,10,Frecommendations are put into action.
OL,12,FSir Sadiq Khan announced that he will
OL,13,Fbe providing a grant of #300,000 from
OL,14,FUK Shared Prosperity Funding in
OL,15,Fsupport of this.
OL,17,FThe report wants nightlife to be
OL,18,Frecognised as part of the culture of
OL,19,Fthe Capital. It offers a plan for a
OL,20,F"truly 24-hour city".
