OL,3,CTaskforce take on problems facing
OL,4,CLondon's late night economy
OL,6,FThis includes improving infrastructure
OL,7,Ffor nightlife spaces and increasing
OL,8,Fthe use of the high street after 6pm.
OL,10,FIt also calls on councils to only
OL,11,Finvestigate noise complaints if a
OL,12,F"minimum of 10 unrelated households"
OL,13,Fcomplain - this is welcomed by
OL,14,FFarringdon pub owner, Harry Smith.
OL,16,FHis community pub, The Sekforde, has
OL,17,Fbeen in a fight to survive after the
OL,18,Fcouncil received a litany of noise
OL,19,Fcomplaints ` almost all of which came
OL,20,Ffrom one angry neighbour.
