OL,3,CTaskforce take on problems facing
OL,4,CLondon's late night economy
OL,6,FHarry said: "Last year we had a
OL,7,Flicense review.
OL,9,F"Some of the things that Islington
OL,10,FCouncil said that they wanted to
OL,11,Fchange on the license would've meant
OL,12,Fwe'd have to close. It was scary,
OL,13,Fscary times.
OL,15,F"They were suggesting that we can't
OL,16,Fallow anybody to stand outside and
OL,17,Fdrink, and we had to reduce the amount
OL,18,Fof people outside so there would only
OL,19,Fbe space for 18 people.
