OL,3,CTaskforce take on problems facing
OL,4,CLondon's late night economy
OL,6,F"In the summertime that would've been
OL,7,Fa nightmare. We wouldn't have been
OL,8,Fable to make the money we need to
OL,9,Fsurvive.
OL,11,F"We have a rule now that people can
OL,12,Fonly sit not stand outside the pub,
OL,13,Fsomeone standing doesn't make more
OL,14,Fnoise that sitting- it's ridiculous."
OL,16,FIn response to the Taskforce's
OL,17,Fproposals, Harry says he is
OL,18,F"skeptical" but hopeful for the
OL,19,Ffuture. He told ITV News London:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
