OL,6,F"It would be nice if there are rules
OL,7,Fin place to say that one person can't
OL,8,Fcreate a problem in a place like ours.
OL,10,F"They need set guidance on what
OL,11,Fconstitutes a nuisance and what
OL,12,Fdoesn't because at the moment it seems
OL,13,Fto be a grey area which neighbours can
OL,14,Fexploit"
OL,16,FThe Taskforce report said that noise
OL,17,Fcomplaints are a "common theme amongst
OL,18,Fvenue owners and operators" and that
OL,19,Fthey often become "a significant point
OL,20,Fof conflict".
