OL,3,CTaskforce take on problems facing
OL,4,CLondon's late night economy
OL,6,FThe London Nightlife Taskforce also
OL,7,Fwant to financially support small
OL,8,Fbusinesses.
OL,10,FThis includes business rates relief
OL,11,Fand support measures, including a
OL,12,Freduced VAT rate.
OL,14,FIt also wants to introduce a London-
OL,15,Fwide licensing standard to bring about
OL,16,Fmore clarity and consistency across
OL,17,Fboroughs.
