OL,3,CTaskforce take on problems facing
OL,4,CLondon's late night economy
OL,6,FThe Taskforce recommendations also aim
OL,7,Fto protect those heading out at night
OL,8,Fand suggests using partnership and
OL,9,Fharm reduction to create safer streets.
OL,11,FIt encourages an independent review of
OL,12,Fthe impact of policing and licensing
OL,13,Fpractices, to ensure that police
OL,14,Fresources are proportionately
OL,15,Fallocated across nightlife areas.
OL,17,FBut the taskforce appreciates harm can
OL,18,Fbe prevented before reaching the
OL,19,Fstreets and encourages the government
OL,20,Fto adapt to an early intervention and
OL,21,Fsupportive public health approach.
