OL,6,FLondon's night-time economy
OL,7,Fcontributes more than #139 billion and
OL,8,Fsupports over a million workers.
OL,10,FThe reports recommendations aim to
OL,11,Fprotect this booming industry and make
OL,12,Fnights out safer and more accessible
OL,13,Ffor everyone- from party goers to
OL,14,Fsmall businesses.
